remarks.para:
The number of diffusion rounds processed in the ciphers transformation method has also been extended, and is user configurable; 
            from the original 16 rounds, to a full 32 rounds of transformation. 
            This increase in key size eliminates brute force attacks, and the increase in the number of diffusion rounds makes cryptanalysis far more difficult.

